CONTEXT DiamondTypeCheck IN ENGLISH

PURPOSE CONTEXT DiamondTypeCheck
{+ Test that diamond operator succeeds when concepts can be matched.
   This verifies the type checker correctly accepts r[A*B]<>s[B*C] yielding [A*C]. +}

RELATION r[A*B]
RELATION s[B*C]
RELATION result[A*C]

RULE testDiamond: result = r<>s

ENDCONTEXT
